Package com.tenio.common.data.common

Class CommonMap

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
java.util.HashMap<String,Object>
com.tenio.common.data.common.CommonMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,Object>
public final class CommonMap extends HashMap<String,Object> implements Serializable
This is an element object class holds data in a map. All message comes from other services will be converted to this object. That helps normalize the way to communicate and be easy to use.
